    <div class="body">
        <p>If an option is set to null,  reset it from the route.</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
// So instead of  this
$this-&gt;view-&gt;url(array('action'=&gt;'edit', 'controller'=&gt;'crud', 'module'=&gt;'users'), null, true );

// we could do that
$this-&gt;view-&gt;url(array('action'=&gt;'edit', 'page'=&gt;null));
</code></pre>

<p>This modification should occur in Zend_Controller_Router_Route</p>

